Chris Warrick has a detailed blog post titled: __"setting-up-a-python-development-environment"__. 
He wrote about topics that can determine if you will ever get to start your first python 
development the right way, or start at all. Some of the topics he wrote about include 
but not limited to the followings:

* Python implementations
* Python distributions
* Installing python
* Installing packages
* Virtual environment
e.t.c

The blog post can be found at: https://chriswarrick.com/blog/2017/07/03/setting-up-a-python-development-environment/
